Description: Retina Associates provides intravitreal injections, lasers, and diagnostic testing services.
Full Description: Retina Associates offers photodynamic therapy, pneumatic retinopexy, and vitreoretinal surgery services. Diagnostic testing services include color fundus photography, fluorescein angiography, ocular coherence tomography, and ultrasound services. Color fundus photography is a digital camera that is used to take photographs of the retina. This is frequently used to document an area of interest in the retina and help guide treatment. A Fluorescein angiography test allows physicians to visualize the blood flow within the eye, much like a conventional angiogram can help a physician see the blood flow in various parts of the body. Dye is injected into a vein in the arm and photographs are taken for approximately ten minutes. The physician then reviews the results and will use them to help guide the treatment.

Rather than an organization trying to sell their surplus equipment to liquidators paying pennies on the dollar, RepowerIT conducts a full inventory of an organizations equipment, testing it to industry standards, determines which items hold resale value and which items aren't worth the time trying to sell, and sells them on behalf of your organization via its network of buyers of such used equipment.  To learn more about the services provided by RepowerIT, contact the company directly.

Description: Creating the SAFEST & LEAST EXPENSIVE automotive connectivity
Headquarters Regions: Greater Philadelphia Area, Great Lakes, Northeastern US
Full Description: Smack Innovations wants to reduce the number of accidents and deaths due to distracted driving.  Specifically, we've developed a way to safely control your smart phone while driving any motor vehicle. SafeConnect is an aftermarket product that a driver can clamp onto any size steering wheel in seconds.  Using SafeConnect, a driver can safely control apps and features of his iPhone or Android phone.  While always keeping hands on the wheel, eyes focused on the road, and phone in his pocket, the driver can push buttons on SafeConnect to dictate text messages, make phone calls, check the local weather, check sports scores, play music, find the cheapest gas station nearby, get directions that avoid traffic, and much more.  Any app on the user’s phone is potentially compatible. Machina research reports automotive mobile connectivity is currently a $22B market growing to $51B by 2018 and $422B by 2022.  By 2022, 1.8 billion automotive connections are predicted (700 million connected cars and 1.1 billion aftermarket devices).  This is a large and rapidly growing market and we have a solution that is safer and less expensive than any other solution on the market. We have patents, working prototypes, a reputable factory willing to mass produce at low cost, and will soon be seeking our first investment - stay tuned!

Full Description: Eye Exams An annual eye examination is an important part of preventive health care. Many eye and vision problems have no obvious signs or symptoms. As a result, individuals are often unaware that problems exist. Early diagnosis and treatment of eye and vision problems are important for maintaining good vision and eye health, and when possible, preventing vision loss. Optical Services Our office offers a full service optical experience for our patients. Our experienced and knowledgeable opticians assist with finding the correct frame styles and lens materials to meet your prescription and lifestyle needs. In-house Lab Our in-house finished lab allows us to do one hour services on most single vision prescriptions dependant on your insurance coverage. Frame adjustments and minor repairs are also completed right here in our office. Contact Lenses Our office fits all types of contact lenses such as soft, RGP, hybrid, multi-focal, mono-vision, and toric lenses. We offer fittings for specialty lenses that can only be found in select private practice offices. Specialty Services Eye To Eye Care offers a variety of specialty services to our patients such as co-management of Lasik and cataract surgeries. Our doctors fit many different types of contact lenses dependent on the needs of our patients, including Duette™ hybrid lenses from SynergEyes®. Check out our specialty services page for more information. Sunglasses and Sports Eyewear Protect your eyes today from our mile-high sun with our large variety of sunglasses and specialty eyewear for all kinds of sports and activities. Products include ski goggles, swim goggles, impact resistant sports goggles and sport sunglasses.

Description: Rural Electric Credit Union is a member-owned financial cooperative offering savings accounts, loans, and other financial services.
Full Description: Florida Rural Electric Credit Union was chartered in December 1975 in order to provide services to rural electric cooperatives in Florida. A member-owned financial cooperative, the credit union provides its members with banking services, including savings and loans. In addition to current members, immediate family members may also join. The Credit Union was housed in the Florida Electric Cooperatives Association building in Tallahassee and provided member service support to the Association. An NCUA-insured financial institution, the Credit Union provides full-service financial services to its members.
